# # [FIX-v60-5] MULTIPLEXED CHECKPOINT SAVING
# #   Save 5 types of checkpoints SEPARATELY (avoid EMA-good-but-RAW-bad issue):
# #     1. best_composite.pth ŌĆö Best composite score (EMA-or-RAW, like v59)
# #     2. best_raw.pth       ŌĆö Best RAW (no-EMA) full-val score [NEW]
# #     3. best_ema.pth       ŌĆö Best EMA full-val score [NEW]
# #     4. best_fast.pth      ŌĆö Best fast-val score per epoch [NEW]
# #     5. best_ade.pth, best_72h.pth, best_ate.pth, best_cte.pth (kept)

# #   At test-time: try BOTH best_raw.pth AND best_ema.pth, pick whichever
# #   scores better on FULL val. This guarantees we never lose to EMA-only fits.

# # [FIX-v60-7] CONFIG CHANGES
# #   - weight_decay 5e-4 ŌåÆ 1e-3 (stronger L2 reg ŌåÆ better generalization)
# #   - val_freq 5 ŌåÆ 3 (catch best states more often)
# #   - patience 25 ŌåÆ 30 (give long-range loss time to converge)
# #   - min_epochs 20 ŌåÆ 25

